data.description: This stately Craftsman sits on a large level corner lot on one of the nicest streets in Bella Vista, near Loch Lomond Marina and Lake Point dining. The Great Room is anchored by a stone fireplace that meets the beamed cathedral ceiling. The chef’s kitchen features Professional Series appliances, gas range, pot filler, custom cabinetry with soft-close doors, topped with beautiful Quartzite counters, teak backsplash, and walk-in pantry. The 3-sided screen porch is perfect year-round spot for grilling and enjoying the wooded views. Split floor plan, each bedroom offering privacy. Private master’s hot tub deck (winter 2019).One bedroom is on the upper level, offering a perfect work-from-home space. All hard surface flooring. Custom binds. Shadowbox privacy fence. Sewered lot with plenty of room for garden, pool, playground. Dual fuel HVAC. Oversized garage + storage building. Builder/designer/agent’s personal home.
